<subSubSection id="C33DCBBF7E6FFFE3FF3F76B4DB65FA0D" pageId="29" pageNumber="28" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B9898347E6FFFE3FF3F76B4DB65FA0D" blockId="29.[192,1440,1438,1526]" pageId="29" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis id="B95344267E6FFFE3FF3F76B4DE46FA4D" bold="true" box="[192,344,1438,1462]" pageId="29" pageNumber="28">Comments.</emphasis>
A genus with surprising phylogenetic placement that yet again indicates the value of DNAbased methods at the genomic scale, and instills confidence in the results due to the large datasets used for phylogeny reconstruction and highly confident nodes in phylogenetic trees.
</paragraph>
